xponents. Sample starts to loose\narsenic at about 1000 K and under vacuum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jun 2013 13:01:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Jul 2013 14:41:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 20 Jul 2013 10:09:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-02"}
