her orders in q. This can be of great utility in building reliable atomistic\nmodels of electromechanical phenomena, as well as for improving the accuracy of\nthe calculation of phonon dispersion curves. Finally, we discuss the physical\ninterpretation of the various contributions to the flexoelectric response,\neither in the static or dynamic regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jun 2013 15:19:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Sep 2013 09:20:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-11-27"}
